txtRollOverPitchFork: In with the new! Use the pitchfork to collect and spread fresh straw.
txtRollOverShovel: Out with the old! Scoop away the soiled straw.
txtShovelHilite2: Use the pitchfork to add new straw for your horse.
txtPitchForkHilite2: First use the shovel to remove the soiled straw.
txtOatsRollOver: Add oats to the trough in front of your horse.
txtHelpTrophyRoom: Click to visit the trophy room.
txtHelpWater: Click to fill the water trough for your thirsty horse.
txtHelpStats: Keep a close eye on your horse's stats!
txtHelpPitchFork: Click to select. Click again to collect straw from the loft. Click once more to spread the new straw on the floor. Repeat until the floor is covered.
txtHelpShovel: Click to select. Click again to scoop dirty straw from your stable. Remove all dirty straw to make room for the new.
txtHelpApple: Click to choose an apple. Carry it to your horse's mouth and click again for a special treat.
txtHelpOats: Click to scoop some oats. Click again to pour them into the feed trough in front of your horse.
txtHelpBottle: Click to grab bottle. Click again near horses's mouth to begin feeding bottle.
txtHelpWorld: Click to go to Bella Sara world.
txtHelpHoofPick: Click to select hoof pick. Click again to pick the mud from each hoof.
txtHelpBrush: Click to select a brush. Click again to gently clean the dust from your horse.
txtNoMoreHay: Well Done! No more fresh straw is needed at this time.
